@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CTracker (base) Primary State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>>   #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>>       #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>>         #0d47a1
    BackgroundColor<<terminal>> #e8f5e9
    BorderColor<<terminal>>     #2e7d32
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "pre_construct" as Pre <<browse>>
state "active" as Active <<browse>>
state "destroyed" as Dead <<terminal>>

Pre -down-> Active : construct(View)
Active --> Active : is_inside(_) [returns TRUE]\non_button_down(_, _) [empty]\non_button_up(_, _) [empty]\non_mouse_move(_, _) [empty]\non_mouse_drag(_, _) [empty]
Active -down-> Dead : destruct

note right of Active
    All 5 mouse handlers have
    EMPTY bodies in the base.
    Subclasses (CRotateTracker,
    CZoomTracker) override.
end note
@enduml
